&lt;p&gt;It&amp;rsquo;s now 22 months since I travelled outside the UK - by far the longest period since university. Although air travel is not exactly sustainable, my experiences travelling for work and pleasure have been very formative, and the sudden halt with few signs of recovery has required some mental readjustment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Obviously I didn&amp;rsquo;t post here as often as I wanted. I&amp;rsquo;m hoping to improve on that in 2022, and have a very full slate this year.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Take care of yourselves and be kind.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Currently playing: Halo Infinite campaign</title><link>https://jonsaville.com/post/2021/12/halo-infinite/</link><pubDate>Mon, 27 Dec 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://jonsaville.com/post/2021/12/halo-infinite/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m playing the Halo Infinite campaign and thoroughly enjoying it. It&amp;rsquo;s a joy to play, with enough narrative to engage you, and an environment that is gorgeous to explore.&lt;/p&gt;






































































