&lt;p&gt;The glitch image was made with the fantastic iOS app &lt;a href="https://apps.apple.com/gb/app/retrospecs/id887031094" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Retrospecs&lt;/a&gt;, and the Hugo shortcode used to embed Mastodon Toots is by &lt;a href="https://www.brycewray.com/posts/2022/06/static-mastodon-toots-hugo/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"&gt;Bryce Wray&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
